com.aliyun.oss.model

类 DeleteVersionsRequest

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.aliyun.oss.model.WebServiceRequest
      • com.aliyun.oss.model.GenericRequest
        • com.aliyun.oss.model.DeleteVersionsRequest

  • public class DeleteVersionsRequest
extends GenericRequest
    Provides options for deleting multiple objects in a specified bucket. Once deleted, the object(s) can only be restored if versioning was enabled when the object(s) was deleted.
    另请参阅:
    OSS.deleteVersions(DeleteVersionsRequest)
